Scenario: Checking the response time after recording an audio message

Bug Description: Audio message takes time to show up after user records the message

Browser: Chrome, Firefox

Environment: https://snatchbot.me/

User Permissions: Valid for all users

Steps to Reproduce: 
1. Navigate to url : https://snatchbot.me/
2. Click on chat bot icon
3. Click on microphone icon to start the recording
4. Allow browser to use the microphone
5. Record the message
6. Click on microphone icon to stop the recording
7. Check the time in which recored message is showing up

Expected Behavior: Recorded message should show up as soon as user stops recording
Actual Behavior: Audio message is taking time to show up after user records the message

Impact: Medium
Priority: Medium

Attachments: Not applicable